Message.message: A Tower turns blue if it has at least one other Tower in its line of sight either vertical or horizontal. Goal: turn all red Towers blue.
Crates break the line of sight. Luckily they can be moved out of the way.
Some Towers can only see horizontally, or only vertically.
Glass can be moved and does not break line of sight.
Some Towers only see in one direction.
Mirrors work how you expect them to.
Horizontal mirrors reflect vertically and do not block horizontal line of sight.
Gray Towers become immobile when they are blue.
Pink mirrors can be rotated by pressing the action (X) button when you are on an adjacent square.
Congratulations!                 You completed all the levels.                                                                           Reward: Bonus Levels
You've activated all the towers!  They don't seem to do anything though...
